  "detailed_description": "\"Pnevmo-Capsula: Domiki\" is a steampunk puzzle game. In the role of a mail trolley, you will have to overcome kilometers of an alternative world. The technologies of this world have developed in a different way, transistors have not been invented, cars are banned, and people move only by rail. You have to play as a small mechanical cart that travels through this world full of classified analog technologies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/e2078907dc69186481cd3dba3a9a7098.poster.avif?t=1713517800\" width=640 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/e2078907dc69186481cd3dba3a9a7098.webm?t=1713517800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/e2078907dc69186481cd3dba3a9a7098.mp4?t=1713517800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The player will dive in many authentic types of Soviet life and interaction with him. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/70304a5b2e72b48d77c6d046961d4e20.poster.avif?t=1713517800\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/70304a5b2e72b48d77c6d046961d4e20.webm?t=1713517800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/70304a5b2e72b48d77c6d046961d4e20.mp4?t=1713517800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Pnevmo-Capsula is an abundance of mechanisms, rails, antennas and a searching for a way out in the puzzle genre.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/0ac7c1dbcd3586849ddcc95bfcf8585e.poster.avif?t=1713517800\" width=640 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/0ac7c1dbcd3586849ddcc95bfcf8585e.webm?t=1713517800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/0ac7c1dbcd3586849ddcc95bfcf8585e.mp4?t=1713517800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "\"Pnevmo-Capsula: Domiki\" is a steampunk puzzle game. In the role of a mail trolley, you will have to overcome kilometers of an alternative world. The technologies of this world have developed in a different way, transistors have not been invented, cars are banned, and people move only by rail. You have to play as a small mechanical cart that travels through this world full of classified analog technologies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/e2078907dc69186481cd3dba3a9a7098.poster.avif?t=1713517800\" width=640 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/e2078907dc69186481cd3dba3a9a7098.webm?t=1713517800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/e2078907dc69186481cd3dba3a9a7098.mp4?t=1713517800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The player will dive in many authentic types of Soviet life and interaction with him. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/70304a5b2e72b48d77c6d046961d4e20.poster.avif?t=1713517800\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/70304a5b2e72b48d77c6d046961d4e20.webm?t=1713517800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/70304a5b2e72b48d77c6d046961d4e20.mp4?t=1713517800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Pnevmo-Capsula is an abundance of mechanisms, rails, antennas and a searching for a way out in the puzzle genre.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/0ac7c1dbcd3586849ddcc95bfcf8585e.poster.avif?t=1713517800\" width=640 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/0ac7c1dbcd3586849ddcc95bfcf8585e.webm?t=1713517800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614380/extras/0ac7c1dbcd3586849ddcc95bfcf8585e.mp4?t=1713517800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
